    • SystemDrive
    • SystemRoot

}
{ Less common variables
  
  table { ll

    `__COMPAT_LAYER` ☰ Setting `__COMPAT_LAYER` to `RunAsInvoker` prevents elevetion and thus also suppresses → Windows/security/User-account-control[UAC] prompts.

  table }

}
